These terms do not imply any other licenses.

## Patent Defense

If you make any written claim that this software infringes or
contributes to infringement of any patent, your patent license
for this software ends immediately. If your company makes such a
claim, your patent license ends immediately for work on behalf of
your company.

## Violations

If you violate these terms, all your licenses end immediately.

